\-j \-\-jobs [jobs]
.
.IP "" 4
.
.nf

Amount of threads used for hashing\. Default: # of CPU threads

One thread can hash one file at a time, potentially speeding up hashing up to `jobs` times\.

No/empty value: # of CPU threads\. \-1: Infinite
.
.fi
.
.IP "" 0
